window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p><strong>NOW A NETFLIX ORIGINAL SERIES</strong></p><p>Lemony Snicket returns with the last book before the last book of his bestselling A Series of Unfortunate Events. Scream and run away before the secrets of the series are revealed!</p><p>Very little is known about Lemony Snicket and A Series of Unfortunate Events. What we do know is contained in the following brief list:</p><ul><li>The books have inexplicably sold millions and millions of copies worldwide</li><li>People in more than 40 countries are consumed by consuming Snicket</li><li>The movie was as sad as the books, if not more so</li><li>Like unrefrigerated butter and fungus, the popularity of these books keeps spreading</li></ul><p>Even less is known about book the twelfth in this alarming phenomenon. What we do know is contained in the following brief list: </p><ul><li>In this book, things only get worse</li><li>Count Olaf is still evil</li><li>The Baudelaire orphans do not win a contest</li><li>The title begins with the word ‘The’</li></ul><p>Sometimes, ignorance is bliss.</p>"; 
